{"tid":1201876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港中學校長會發聲明不贊成師生罷課","createTime":"2019-06-11T07:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T08:29:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":210,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"166184b825a7978ccf9b6a8a68538c67873285de","tid":1201876,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:00:10.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港中學校長會發聲明，不贊成師生罷課，希望政府暫緩修訂逃犯條例，避免社會對立惡化。校長會表示，因有校長反映校內學生因修例感到不滿，醞釀罷課而主動發聲明。<br />\n香港中學校長會執委會發表題為「守護學生福祉」的聲明，表示極度關注社會因政府建議修訂逃犯條例出現的社會爭拗，及對學生身心發展的影響。校長會不贊成師生以罷課表達訴求，深盼政府暫緩立法，廣泛聆聽民意，避免社會對立惡化。同時，呼籲教育同工謹守崗位，守護學生褔祉。<br />\n校長會表示，從不少校長得知校內學生因今次政府修例感到不滿，醞釀罷課，因此主動發出今次聲明。<br />\n由全國人大代表黃友嘉出任榮譽會長的香港校董學會發聲明，譴責有人鼓動罷課、罷考，對學校、社會之破壞力難以估計，並對這些別有用心、行為惡毒鼓動這種類「新文革」的人予以最嚴厲的譴責。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/r1f.AtshpSNyNF2wwZt5GA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/FUG-PRINCIPAL-190611-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fr1f.AtshpSNyNF2wwZt5GA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FFUG-PRINCIPAL-190611-12.jpg&h=9826b67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢班校長真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%8D%E8%B4%8A%E6%88%90%E5%B8%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2-040758935.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B